  <p>Searching for mental health support means encountering a bewildering number of professional titles: therapist, counselor, psychologist, psychiatrist, social worker, psychoanalyst. These aren't interchangeable, and choosing the right type of professional for your situation matters.</p>
  <p>This guide explains each title, what they can and can't do, and who you should seek out for your specific needs.</p>
